        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Realizing the Economic Opportunities and Value of Expanding Recycling Act or the RECOVER Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to establish a Recycling Infrastructure Program. Under the program, the EPA may award financial assistance to states, local governments, and tribal governments to support and expand their recycling infrastructure and programs.</p>]]>
        </text>
